Observations/Takeaways Cont.
- Brand equity and culture are so intertwined.  The authenticity of a project can be defined by the types of partnerships secured.  For me @AngryPitbullCLB has so much clarity when it comes to what is "on brand". #APC #Hoodville #Hennessy

Observations/Takeaways Cont.
- Better Web2 mousetraps seem doomed in Web3.  Reimagining what the world 'could be' is the promise; not incremental change.  For me @nudiecommunity is demonstrating that at scale with their all female team. #NudieCommunity #SendNudies #WomeninNFTs

Observations/Takeaways Cont.
- Communities come in all shapes and sizes.  Discord activity is a valuable signal, however it's not everything.  For me @BALLERZ_NFT tapped into a 90's video game nostalgia and hoop culture. #Ballerz #BallerzNation #BallerzFollowBallerz

Observations/Takeaways:
- Project discovery is rather messy & full of friction.  I still believe WoM recommendations is the best way to go for people new to this space.
- Twitter Spaces is a solid solution for due diligence.  Listening to someone speak can tell you all you need.
